response.original_title: Los Caminantes: Lo Mas Chulo, Chulo, Chulo
response.overview: Music & Musicals, Latin Music, Traditional Latin Music - For more than 20 years, Guanajuato, Mexico, natives Los Caminantes have delighted fans with a stream of hit songs and memorable live concerts. Their music has transcended the borders of their homeland and has garnered the band a fan base that stretches from the United States to South America. This collection of six video hits includes "Jaula Dorada," "Baraja Adicta," "Sin un Adios," "Ven y Abrazame," "Amor sin Palabras" and "Todo Me Gusta de Ti."
response.title: Los Caminantes: Lo Mas Chulo, Chulo, Chulo
